                "type": "math",
                "latex": "\\begin{aligned}\n4PQ &= (x^2+z^2-y^2)(x^2+y^2-z^2),\\\\\n4QR &= (x^2+y^2-z^2)(y^2+z^2-x^2),\\\\\n4RP &= (y^2+z^2-x^2)(x^2+z^2-y^2).\n\\end{aligned}"
